BODY FIXER: Field medic and surgeon of the wastelands

The Body Fixer is a field medic and surgeon who keeps warriors alive
across the Rifts wastelands. Armed with genuine medical training and
scientific knowledge, they are one of the most valued characters in any
group.

Body Fixers receive a complete medical and scientific skill base from
the start, choosing from Medical, Science, Technical, and Physical
categories. They are not combat-focused but their value in the field is
immeasurable.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: IQ 12, ME 8.
  Equipment: Surgical kit, portable medical scanner, drug and bandage
    kit, concealed sidearm, medical ID credentials, and doctor's bag.

